WorkItem.Description:
Page margins are not working in 1.7.8, using either mPDF or domPDF.  Margins are correct in Excel5, as setting them like so:

    $pageMargins = $sheet->getPageMargins();
    $pageMargins->setTop('.25');
    $pageMargins->setBottom('.25');
    $pageMargins->setLeft('.2');
    $pageMargins->setRight('.2');

works perfectly.  Switching the output to PDF gives margins of ~1" all around. I have had no success in finding a way to pass margins to mPDF itself from PHPExcel.
